set public.

00:32:51.000 --> 00:32:54.110
So for example, my birthdate
is set public, but my home

00:32:54.110 --> 00:32:54.550
address isn't.

00:32:54.550 --> 00:32:56.740
So a developer would be able to
actually get my birthday,

00:32:56.740 --> 00:32:58.510
