00:33:02.620 --> 00:33:06.270
And the age range and the
preferred language.

00:33:06.270 --> 00:33:09.060
And all that falls under our
data retention policy.

00:33:09.060 --> 00:33:11.510
You have to keep a fresh cache
of the data, and if the user

00:33:11.510 --> 00:33:13.430
